# About

Hello! I'm Lautaro Acosta Quintana, a programmer from Argentina. I'm currently pursuing an Information Systems Engineering degree at [UTN](https://www.frre.utn.edu.ar/). You can find my résumé in [English](https://cdn.lautaroacosta.com/resume_us_2.pdf) or [Spanish](https://cdn.lautaroacosta.com/resume_es_2.pdf).

I love to code and I can't help but to [ask questions](https://jvns.ca/blog/good-questions/), and because of that, I write at length about the things I find interesting.
